{"id": 1857, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得当下的人们在追求“慢”这件事上有哪些跑偏？", "description": "迷恋“从前的日色变得慢，车马邮件都慢”……那你还想不想收快递了！（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 14495, "comment_count": 50, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170816180134I1UyYZL5fCAn3o9v.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-20T17:00:31Z", "questions": [{"id": 2819, "title": "你觉得当下的人们在追求“慢”这件事上有哪些跑偏？", "content": "现如今，你见到过哪些关于“慢”的误解？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 229963, "content": "分不清懒和慢：工作一段时间之后，无论如何都需要gap休息一下", "image": "img/option/option/20170817134452LCjscz0PKwbay6l7.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229964, "content": "有情怀，不谈钱：把开旅店、咖啡馆当成慢生活，不挣钱也行", "image": "img/option/option/201708171346486donCLkYWVSxlq0s.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229971, "content": "反竞争：对不合理的事情不争不抢，做一个恬淡的人，岁月静好", "image": "img/option/option/20170817135921csTx60uGbN5AQKyV.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229980, "content": "固定套路：花一整天去做个手工皮具、插花什么的才叫精致生活方式", "image": "img/option/option/20170817141758p6MfQhSqENgyDHR8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229986, "content": "找初心，找自己：去西藏净化灵魂，慢递一张明信片给自己", "image": "img/option/option/20170817160555AX1LyVkKHBUepNun.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229989, "content": "反工业化：手作衣物、手工肥皂、天然草本护肤品一定比工业化制品好", "image": "img/option/option/20170817144009BtnWgxRhCD7lNYTw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230011, "content": "反新科技：追捧按键手机、写信，死活不读电子书之类的", "image": "img/option/option/20170817161827bJd2mgF6LGCer9p3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229990, "content": "花式养生：慢煮健康餐，枸杞威士忌", "image": "img/option/option/20170817144311QWGunr18jHCi4gXa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230515, "content": "总之无论如何就是要离开城市：下乡，进山，离开喧嚣找静谧", "image": "img/option/option/201708201116197IVyHxbq8iRFEOlB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}